'''Shadorians''' was the name of the residents of [[Shador]], whether they were native or not. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] interacted with an [[Avogwi]] Shadorian when he visited the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] shortly after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]]. Shadorians were noted as [[Assassin/Legends|assassins]].

